---
---
<header class="masthead">
  <h1 class="reveal reveal-1">Nuh<span class="dash">—</span>Muh</h1>
</header>

<style>
  .masthead { padding: 5.5rem 0 3.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .masthead h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Unicase', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 13vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: inline-block;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .masthead h1 .dash {
    color: var(--mark);
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .masthead h1:hover .dash { transform: translateX(0.1em) rotate(-3deg); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .masthead { padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem; } }
</style>
